text: Ayouba Traoré (born 9 August 1982) is a heavyweight judoka from Mali. He competed at the 2016 Summer Olympics, in the 100 kg category, and was eliminated by Cyrille Maret in the first bout. Traoré works at a French international school in Bamako.Ayouba Traoré . nbcolympics.com ==References== Category:1982 births Category:Living people Category:Malian male judoka Category:Olympic judoka of Mali Category:Judoka at the 2016 Summer Olympics
